      roleTitle: "Business Analyst | Product Operations & Strategy",
      slogan:
        "Built 0-to-1 analytics infrastructure to translate investor, customer, and executive requirements into operational roadmap trade-offs and high-retention product alignment.",
      friction:
        "A rapidly scaling real estate platform operated with fragmented data streams and disconnected workflows. Product development, sales, and leadership lacked a centralized source of truth, resulting in misaligned property-matching algorithms and isolated communication channels.",
