      "I delivered 8+ cross-functional initiatives by coordinating 10+ stakeholders, tracking more than 50 milestones, and making project health visible through dashboards and weekly reporting across 15+ metrics. The biggest shift was reducing fragmentation: 80 separate artifacts became 27 standardized assets that teams could actually use.",
    growthStory:
      "The work was high leverage because adoption depended on clarity, not just execution. Facilitating 25+ workshops and training 50+ users taught me how to make process change feel usable at scale: clear ownership, clean materials, visible risks, and enough structure for global teams to move together.",
    artifacts: ["Revenue operations", "KPI dashboards", "Process governance", "Enablement"],
    caseStudy: {
      roleTitle: "Senior Business Process Analyst | Revenue Operations",
      slogan:
        "Engineered global financial governance, closed the gap between audit policy and live-system automation, and unified process models across global teams.",
      friction:
        "Global Accounts Receivable (AR) approval cycles spanned AMER, EMEA, and APAC with manual workflows and stale data. This disconnect created critical compliance risks and an operational lag between approved financial governance policies and live-system transaction execution.",
      play: [
        {
          lead: "Sole Program Driver",
          text: "Owned the end-to-end execution of the Global AR Approval and Adjustments Matrix governance cycle, restructuring complex payment plan thresholds mid-cycle under tight SOX pressure.",
        },
        {
          lead: "Systems Alignment",
          text: "Bridged the gap between manual controls and systems by raising and coordinating automated system change tickets in 1Finance and 1GBO to eliminate processing lag.",
        },
        {
          lead: "Global Asset Standardization",
          text: "Standardized and consolidated over 80 fragmented global operational assets down to 27 highly governed, audit-ready playbooks.",
        },
      ],
      leverage: [
        {
          lead: "100% Audit-Ready Compliance",
          text: "Maintained flawless SOX-grade financial governance, removing gaps by retiring stale approvers globally.",
        },
        {
          lead: "Zero-Lag System Behavior",
          text: "Completely eliminated manual compliance delays; live transactional behaviors now update instantly alongside policy publication.",
        },
        {
          lead: "Set the Quality Gold Standard",
          text: 'Designed a rotating audit scorecard framework targeting "why" rather than "what," establishing the standard benchmark for executive AR readouts.',
        },
      ],
      metric: {
        value: "80 → 27",
        label: "Fragmented legacy assets streamlined into clean, standardized global playbooks.",
      },
      comparison: [
        {
          before: "Fragmented, manual AR approvals across 3 regions",
          after: "1 Standardized Global AR Matrix with clear ownership",
          tools: ["1Finance", "1GBO"],
        },
        {
          before: "Passive dashboards with limited executive visibility",
          after: "Active Scorecard-Based Governance mapped to V2MOM",
          tools: ["Tableau", "KPI Models"],
        },
